{"tid":555803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【90後老屎忽玩回憶】痴線以前香港啲動畫歌詞填得仲好過林夕","createTime":"2018-02-10T00:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T00:59:38.000Z","uid":165817,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"39ec17314e4b392fdee6e42b3ce69df40653204b","tid":555803,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:31:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">「本應伴著晚空孤單一個走，竟可有你挽手四面環遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081638_2ebaaf1bf5a8fdcd9962e926c98194e2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081638_2ebaaf1bf5a8fdcd9962e926c98194e2.jpeg&h=40675542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到咁感性嘅歌詞，點會諗到係幾隻電腦怪獸嘅碌咭卡通片？但其實，呢句先係最代表到套動畫嘅歌詞。相信好多男孩子都覺得，呢套野最正嘅唔只係劇情，而係拍檔之間嘅互相扶持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">「為何凌晨零時想起你？這幻覺極奇妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081639_d46755a03d48799e483f2d6f4408c283.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081639_d46755a03d48799e483f2d6f4408c283.jpeg&h=767ef809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信唔少女仔細個都有追呢套卡通片，聽到呢句嘅時候，甚至會諗起自己暗戀嘅男仔。香港情歌泛濫，但可能卻唔夠呢句嚟得簡單有力，一語道破少女心事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「在我懷抱裏，沒有寒風吹，從來未懂得空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081639_5ab114f4552011c68cfe8bca878be341.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081639_5ab114f4552011c68cfe8bca878be341.jpeg&h=3ab69e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個系列嘅動畫，喺香港動畫歌嚟講真係填得宇宙級咁精彩。先唔講套卡通本身有幾熱血，淨係唱呢句俾女朋友聽，攬住佢話會保護佢，都已經冧死佢，真係好過唱我的宣言。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">「未勇敢學飛，情緒都會飛，漆黑都可感應你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081640_95d7b99ebb993fce986a2f21c1ffa17d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081640_95d7b99ebb993fce986a2f21c1ffa17d.jpeg&h=f9216157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就算我只係一個渺小嘅細路女，我都因為要保護你而變得勇敢；就算全世界都睇你唔到，世界末日我都一樣搵到你。因為，我哋係拍檔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「有真心的知己齊同路，多麼高興，你送我最響亮笑聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081640_46c02bbf5fe32ad0e7623974c23185c1.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081640_46c02bbf5fe32ad0e7623974c23185c1.jpeg&h=bc66d494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前嘅動畫歌詞，強調嘅唔係打打殺殺、唔係情節有幾好睇，而係強調同伴、友情。雖然呢句有少少老土，但係聽到嗰陣，真係想打個電話，多謝下身邊嗰位好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">「坐上火箭，和繁星飛出天際訴心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081640_f49cac049e3a7c56b7b3c3a4219205ec.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081640_f49cac049e3a7c56b7b3c3a4219205ec.jpeg&h=434ec801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地細個鍾意睇卡通片，因為可以俾我地放肆去幻想同發夢。只要敢想像，再天馬行空嘅事，一樣有可能發生。人大咗，反而好似唔記得咗呢個道理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「請鍛煉你的英勇，能同遊星空。縱辛苦，不過願望不會一剎落了空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081640_f8f01ae365acc9aa87ae9e10b7467178.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081640_f8f01ae365acc9aa87ae9e10b7467178.jpeg&h=6ac86b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除咗友情嘅熱血教人動容之外，動畫歌最重要嘅元素，當然唔少得勵志啦。成長路上，我地會遇到好多挫折同困難，但只要勇敢面對，始終會見到願望達成嘅一日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">「想不走也找不到藉口，深谷裏找到出口，當中一把聲音帶我出走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081641_9a1ec9ee9cf7772e0e3bb143355068a6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081641_9a1ec9ee9cf7772e0e3bb143355068a6.jpeg&h=3b1cef69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為二千年代中期最受歡迎嘅動畫，呢首歌嘅歌詞看似同其他動畫好唔同，寫得深入好多、陰暗好多。但其實帶俾小朋友嘅訊息都一樣：遇到唔如意嘅事，最重要爬返起身，離開低谷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「若是流汗，流向觀眾席裏。這次輸了，不要流眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/10/081641_236b64983d87efc83c7a9e16a87d7cf0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F10%2F081641_236b64983d87efc83c7a9e16a87d7cf0.jpeg&h=41267d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後，當然唔少得呢首已經跨越動漫界、去到全香港人經常攞嚟打氣嘅神曲。嗰種熱血程度係，就算你唔知咩係越位，都一樣會被佢感染，變哂韋拉堅尼咁，成團火燃燒哂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n望返上面咁多位歌手嘅近照，都發現佢地都老咗唔少，唔再係以前嗰個打住青春形象唱歌俾小朋友聽嘅後生仔女。而我地，都一步步遠離我哋嘅青春。<br />\n<br />\n以前嘅動畫歌，一聽就好熱血，亦都易記又膾炙人口，有齊哂成為經典歌所需嘅元素。除咗因為日本嘅音樂人寫得好之外，都要多謝香港填詞人寫咗好多足以媲美唔少流行金曲嘅歌詞。<br />\n<br />\n永遠都會記得電視台仍然好重視外購動畫主題曲嘅年代：請四大天王唱、搞兒歌頒獎禮、填好精彩嘅歌詞......<br />\n<br />\n而家電視台對動畫嘅重視程度，同十五年前已經冇得比。唔好話想聽陳奕迅劉德華郭富城吖，而家想聽到句廣東話都難。<br />\n<br />\n真係好慶幸自己趕得切喺九十年代出世，趕到呢個精彩世代嘅尾班車。Anyway，有冇巴絲認到哂上面嘅係咩歌同咩卡通？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9bbf15ce46bc0c93cb21f7c9bc04577fc29bf90","tid":555803,"uid":164184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:33:26.000Z","msg":"啲相咩事"},{"pid":"787bb3a7431cbe058668091ffed63f18152ff4ed","tid":555803,"uid":148723,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"點解啲相咁恐怖"},{"pid":"152ef03958cb7fd5494c8373cc021913f7124af2","tid":555803,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"787bb3a7431cbe058668091ffed63f18152ff4ed","tid":555803,"uid":148723,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"點解啲相咁恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咩"},{"pid":"139b568a81d565ea3d4ebb67cb76e33ffedba228","tid":555803,"uid":19888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:41:00.000Z","msg":"林峯個首應該係呢句 露營必須酒"},{"pid":"ef2b34aff95777357e4cbbc6a4725213ba762468","tid":555803,"uid":150098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:41:00.000Z","msg":"好耐之前有套卡通片＂時空歷險記＂首歌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6fb3ff338b2a1ca26a19beb929a59e3cd10899","tid":555803,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef2b34aff95777357e4cbbc6a4725213ba762468","tid":555803,"uid":150098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:41:00.000Z","msg":"好耐之前有套卡通片＂時空歷險記＂首歌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"係咪薛凱琪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a3ff31efe400ffe267738be43033f2e9d8eb6f","tid":555803,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:48:12.000Z","msg":"外星bb撞地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似戴夢夢啫<br />\n仲有守護甜心 王君馨"},{"pid":"99acc754d7d2606bf43c9fa57178bef8316b689d","tid":555803,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:51:40.000Z","msg":"好正咩？有回憶加乘咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e15d7d19a62193121ae8bb0cf84d5887d649a4","tid":555803,"uid":57524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db6fb3ff338b2a1ca26a19beb929a59e3cd10899","tid":555803,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef2b34aff95777357e4cbbc6a4725213ba762468","tid":555803,"uid":150098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:41:00.000Z","msg":"好耐之前有套卡通片＂時空歷險記＂首歌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"係咪薛凱琪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:57:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4l-PwTxvxCo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4l-PwTxvxCo&d=9kWRrrbm%2Fk7%2Bxn%2BO0qEwoDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=cc4f795a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4l-PwTxvxCo</a><br />\n<br />\n識貨之人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e568537b160c2895bbfb4467a843f64c320a8931","tid":555803,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T00:59:38.000Z","msg":"大家唔好回呢個啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我喺動漫台開返個正常po<br />\n呢個由佢沉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/555811/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/555811/page/1</a>"}]}